Who are we? 
We are a marketing & consultancy company, made to guide enterprises, entrepreneurs and companies
to find affiliate networks, form strategic partnerships and achieve their global goals in the markets that 
we have specialized in. Our excellence lies in the fact that we are very experienced with different customer groups 
and their behaviours.
Founded and based in Berlin, we have strong ties and networks in many European, Middle Eastern and also some Asian markets.
We offer help in languages, including but not limited to English, German, Turkish, Farsi and Arabic. 
